       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    PSI49302.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA PSI49302.
      *
      *     AprovacaoColegialWS
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE PSI49302         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY PSCV4930.
       COPY PSCV4931.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY VSCK0001.
       COPY VSCK0002.
      *
       COPY ARCK0001.
       COPY ARCK0002.
       COPY AQCW0005.
       COPY VIAW0020.
       COPY ETCL0002.
       COPY VIAL9001.
      *
       COPY PSCL5810.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME            PIC  X(08) VALUE 'PSI49302'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE PSI49302         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO PSCV4930-MSG.
           MOVE PSCV4930-ASE       TO PSCV4931-ASE.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE PSCV4930-ADE       TO PSCV4931-ADE.



           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-OBTEM-DADOS
                 THRU 2299-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF

           .
       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2200-OBTEM-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-OBTEM-DADOS.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2200-OBTEM-DADOS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE PSCL5810-COMMAREA    REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                                ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.

           SET  PSCL5810-CANCELAR-PROCESSO TO TRUE.

           MOVE PSCV4930-GUSER             TO PSCL5810-GUSER.
           MOVE PSCV4930-MONTANTE          TO PSCL5810-NMONTANTE.
           MOVE PSCV4930-NCLIENTE          TO PSCL5810-NCLI.
           MOVE PSCV4930-PID               TO PSCL5810-PID.

           PERFORM ETCP0002-FORM-ONLINE-IN
              THRU ETCP0002-FORM-ONLINE-IN-EXIT.

           PERFORM CALL-PSM5810
              THRU CALL-PSM5810-EXIT

           PERFORM ETCP0002-STD-END
              THRU ETCP0002-STD-END-EXIT

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE ETCL0002-RCODE          TO VIAW0020-RCODE

              PERFORM VIAP0020-TRATA-RCODE
                 THRU VIAP0020-TRATA-RCODE-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE PSCL5810-GUSER       TO PSCV4931-GUSER
              MOVE PSCL5810-NMONTANTE   TO PSCV4931-MONTANTE
              MOVE PSCL5810-NCLI        TO PSCV4931-NCLIENTE
              MOVE PSCL5810-PID         TO PSCV4931-PID
              MOVE PSCL5810-TSTATUS     TO PSCV4931-TSTATUS
              MOVE PSCL5810-TREGISTOS   TO PSCV4931-TREGISTOS
              MOVE PSCL5810-DTPARECER   TO PSCV4931-DTPARECER
              MOVE PSCL5810-STATUSAP    TO PSCV4931-STATUSAP
              MOVE PSCL5810-STATUSQ     TO PSCV4931-STATUSQ
              MOVE PSCL5810-WSOUT       TO PSCV4931-WSOUT
              MOVE PSCL5810-IDCANCEL    TO PSCV4931-IDCANCEL
           ELSE
              MOVE ETCL0002-IND-ERROS
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE VSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                TO PSCV4931-PID-S
              MOVE ETCL0002-CAPLIC-ERRO
                TO PSCV4931-PID-CAPLIC
              MOVE ETCL0002-NR-ERRO
                TO PSCV4931-PID-MSG
           END-IF.

       2299-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE PSCV4931-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE PSCV4931-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE PSCV4931-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0016.
           COPY AQCP0005.
           COPY ETCP0002.
           COPY VIAP0020.
           COPY PSCP5810.
